      "title": "Abrindo a Colmeia",
      "type": "scene",
      "transition": "fade",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "position": 0,
          "character_id": "in2_c1",
          "text": "Exato! A fumaça imita sinal de incêndio — as abelhas enchem o papo de mel pra fugir e ficam dóceis. Um truque que usa o instinto natural delas.",
          "audio_url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/funifier/games/69c58d24e6650e26dad21537/story_audio/69ea494db5fee93883c2e618_story-tts-69ea494db5fee93883c2e617.mp3",
          "_ttsGenerating": false,
          "_audioDuration": 9
        },
        {
          "position": 1,
          "text": "Com a técnica certa, Pedro abre a primeira colmeia. As abelhas continuam trabalhando, sem agitação.",
          "audio_url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/funifier/games/69c58d24e6650e26dad21537/story_audio/69ea4952b5fee93883c2e61c_story-tts-69ea4952b5fee93883c2e61b.mp3",
          "_ttsGenerating": false,
          "_audioDuration": 6.168
        },
        {
          "position": 2,
          "character_id": "in2_c2",
          "text": "Olha que lindo! Todo o favo cheio. Mas será que está no ponto?",
          "audio_url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/funifier/games/69c58d24e6650e26dad21537/story_audio/69ea4956b5fee93883c2e61e_story-tts-69ea4956b5fee93883c2e61d.mp3",
